document_data.mainbody:
'''''Spelljammer: AD&D Adventures in Space''''' is a supplement that introduces the Spelljammer campaign setting for AD&D 2{{nd}} edition. It contains a comprehensive description of several worlds, including [[Realmspace]] and the [[Forgotten Realms]].

{{quote|
''Multitudes of worlds wheel through [[Wildspace]]. The [[Crystal sphere|crystal shell]]s that encase them bob and drift in a turbulent, rainbow ocean which fills all the cosmos. Sturdy merchants, bold pirates, and daring explorers venture into the great, unknown vastness of the universe, seeking wealth and adventure.''

''The SPELLJAMMER Game puts you in command of a fantastic ship capable of spanning the tremendous distances between planets. Graceful [[elf|elven]] flitters, stately [[illithid]] galleys, deadly [[beholder]] tyrants, and the awesome ''Spelljammer'' itself carry trade, emissaries, and heroic action throughout all the worlds of the AD&D game.''
}}
